<plot>Roy Atwell, and his stuttering juxtaposition of the King's English, makes a return of films in this RKO Radio-Flash short which finds Roy shopping for a present to give his wife. He meets department-store salesgirl Marion Martin who is demonstrating aluminum cooking-ware, and he buys a set for his wife. A gossipy neighbor is nearby and hotfoots it to Roy's home and reports he is flirting with a blonde in a department store. His wife leaves and goes home to Mother. Marion shows up do give a demonstration on how to use the cooking-ware. His wife decides to return and arrives at their apartment at the same time Marion's jealous boyfriend shows up. A remake of a remake that would be remade again..and again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074161</url></doc>
